{"tid":2371666,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"辯方：警雷射筆照眼逼少年認罪","createTime":"2021-01-19T04:56:22.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-19T05:03:09.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6f195ef48813eca71bf01eacc7c77ab297b4b202","tid":2371666,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T04:56:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210119/XEZ23OBAWRHMXHUKBCAABOH5JU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210119%2FXEZ23OBAWRHMXHUKBCAABOH5JU%2F&d=aWm579aYkHvvwdD7ZyOwrL9EqtgOipuK5hw8%2B6jdv%2Bo%3D&h=38225fb7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210119%2FXEZ23OBAWRHMXHUKBCAABOH5JU%2F&h=1c82e8b2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210119/XEZ23OBAWRHMXHUKBCAABOH5JU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n辯方：警雷射筆照眼逼少年認罪<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/TB7SR2o5WmJwJV3ek_yiyrR33xo=/638x359/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/INTPBKDU3RHRDG2XMXLCSVHUOY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FTB7SR2o5WmJwJV3ek_yiyrR33xo%3D%2F638x359%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FINTPBKDU3RHRDG2XMXLCSVHUOY.jpg&h=40da01b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警長曾華偉<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】前年10月7日有示威者在觀塘一帶集結，多人被捕，當中一名15歲少年被指破壞港鐵升降機昨受審。休班警供稱，當晚他在觀塘站外發現約十名撐傘示威者包圍升降機，但他僅能在傘縫看到有人用硬物破壞幕牆，看不到破壞者的衣着容貌或破壞情況。此外，辯方反對少年的招認口供呈堂，指有事主遭警長用警棍打及雷射筆射眼，逼承認犯案。<br />\n<br />\n現已。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n辯方反對招認口供呈堂<br />\n<br />\n辯方昨反對將少年的招認口供呈堂，指警員查問前沒施警誡或要求少年監護人陪同，當晚制服少年的警長曾華偉用警棍打他，威嚇他認破壞涉案升降機，更用雷射筆照其眼睛；少年最終就範。少年父亦在警長誤導下，加簽兒子的招認口供。<br />\n<br />\n警長曾華偉供稱，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n現職國安處的警長羅致中供稱，當日他到達觀塘站時，現場已沒人破壞。辯方指少年見到警員後即舉手示意不反抗，但曾華偉仍用警棍打及推跌他；羅不同意。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：KTCC412/20"},{"pid":"9265cd5eafc84b23be0a7af734ccec0fc7b55392","tid":2371666,"uid":14422,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T05:00:04.000Z","msg":"現職國安處的警長羅致中"},{"pid":"9406c0510baf88a8b4717be6016f5b426a52230a","tid":2371666,"uid":9193,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T05:03:09.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>國安處警長羅致中</strong></span></span>"}]}